	the show to meet the performers—you’ll be able to say\\\, “I saw them befo
	re they were famous!” \\n6:00pm: Chad Sunday 300\\\, Bestock 400\\\, Tim 4
	00\\\, Tony 500\\n8:00pm: Chad Monday 300\\\, Chazz 400\\\, Laurel 400\\\,
